// --- VALUE TYPES ---
//
// --- Literals ---
// lit => following value is a literal. Will be converted like this:
//     ... lit   F => 0x000F instead of 0x0046
//
// Multi-character literals will also be taken as is:
//     ... lit D4B => 0x0D4B
//
// Literals can also just be hexadecimal values:
//     ... lit 0xF0F0
//
// --- Hexadecimals ---
// hex => following value will be converted to its hexadecimal representation:
//     ... hex U => 0x0055

load A hex U
load X hex W
load Y hex U
